 the ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":"front end for the TON blockchain","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":", a Layer 1 crypto network with 1 billion potential users built-in.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Imagine if WhatsApp had a built-in crypto wallet where you could send Bitcoin as easily as sending a text. That's what Telegram + TON is building. And it's already live.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Pro Tip","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":": If you're in crypto and not on Telegram, you're missing 80% of the alpha. Every new token launch, every airdrop, every insider signal - it all happens on Telegram first.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"heading-2","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"How Does Telegram Actually Work? (And Why It's Different)","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Most people think Telegram is just WhatsApp with better privacy. Not quite.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"heading-3","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Feature 1: Cloud-Based (Not Phone-Based)","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"WhatsApp ties your account to your phone number and device. Lose your phone? Lose your chat history.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Telegram stores everything in the cloud. You can log in from your laptop, tablet, or new phone instantly - all your messages sync across devices.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Real-World Scenario:","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":" You're traveling. Your phone gets stolen. On WhatsApp, you're scre